OL,6,FThe Queen's death was announced after 
OL,7,Falmost six hours of rolling news on BBC
OL,8,FOne.                                  
OL,10,FThe simple fact that Buckingham Palace
OL,11,Fhad issued a statement on the Queen's 
OL,12,Fhealth was a sign that there was      
OL,13,Fserious concern  even though the words
OL,14,Fof the statement itself did not convey
OL,15,Fthe gravity of the situation.         
OL,17,FThe fact a statement was made by the  
OL,18,FSpeaker of the House of Commons was   
OL,19,Falso a sign of real concern.          
OL,3,CWell-rehearsed procedures invoked for 
OL,4,CRoyal news coverage                   
OL,22,                                  G2/10
