PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F347A1664222673
OL,6,FThe decision to interrupt Bargain Hunt
OL,7,Fand stay with rolling news through the
OL,8,Fafternoon would not have been taken   
OL,9,Flightly.                              
OL,11,FAt this point, it is worth noting that
OL,12,Fthe procedure for interrupting        
OL,13,Fprogrammes appears to have changed.   
OL,15,FIt now seems to be the case that a    
OL,16,Fprogramme will simply be faded to black
OL,17,Fand that the news presenter will      
OL,18,Fwelcome viewers to BBC One.           
OL,3,CWell-rehearsed procedures invoked for 
OL,4,CRoyal news coverage                   
