OL,6,FOf course, in the past Presentation   
OL,7,Fwould put up a slide and the announcer
OL,8,Fwould hand to the newsroom.           
OL,10,FAs the afternoon progressed, it was   
OL,11,Fnoticeable that Huw Edwards and many  
OL,12,Freporters were wearing black. Clearly 
OL,13,Fthe possibility of an announcement was
OL,14,Fon their minds.                       
OL,16,FHowever, until 5pm, ITV was running as
OL,17,Fnormal. There were no news reports or 
OL,18,Fchanges to the schedule although one  
OL,19,Fstory dominated the ITV Lunchtime News.
