OL,6,FThe announcement of Her Majesty's death
OL,7,Fcame around 6.32pm and was made by Huw
OL,8,FEdwards during the rolling news       
OL,9,Fprogramme which had replaced the normal
OL,10,FBBC News at Six.                      
OL,12,FA few moments later, BBC Two joined  
OL,13,Fan abrupt fade to black came during   
OL,14,Fathletics coverage.                   
OL,16,FAgain it is noticeable the caption came
OL,17,Ffrom News  not Presentation  and that
OL,18,FHuw made the out-of-vision announcement
OL,19,Fabout programmes being interrupted.   
OL,20,FThis would have been in the planned   
OL,21,Fprocedures.                           
