OL,6,FBy Friday morning, some of BBC One's  
OL,7,Fnormal programmes had moved to BBC Two.
OL,8,FNaturally care will need to be taken to
OL,9,Fensure nothing inappropriate is       
OL,10,Faccidentally shown.                   
OL,12,FBBC One will resume some normal       
OL,13,Fprogramming from this evening but the 
OL,14,Fchannel will have a more subdued      
OL,15,Fcharacter during the period leading up
OL,16,Fto the State Funeral. It is reasonable
OL,17,Fto expect anything too lighthearted   
OL,18,Fwill be dropped.                      
