OL,6,FPresentation needs to be on guard     
OL,7,Fagainst the risk of a misplaced trailer
OL,8,For misjudged transition causing       
OL,9,Fdifficulties.                         
OL,11,FIn days gone by, things would have been
OL,12,Fdifferent.                            
OL,14,FFormer announcer Reg Sanders tweeted a
OL,15,Fpicture of the caption placed in the  
OL,16,FNoddy machine for the death of the    
OL,17,FQueen.                                
