OL,6,FThings are going to be a bit different
OL,7,Fon BBC TV for the next few days. We   
OL,8,Frehearsed for this moment so many times
OL,9,Fover the years. This caption is from  
OL,10,FThe Noddy camera system.              
OL,11,Fpic.twitter.com/3n3qY1ibip            
OL,13,FExactly how it may have been used is  
OL,14,Fnot clear. Perhaps Reg or another     
OL,15,Fformer member of Pres staff can offer 
OL,16,Fan insight?                           
OL,18,FBut I would imagine that in those days
OL,19,Fa procedure like the following would  
OL,20,Fhave been adopted.                    
