OL,6,FAfter the news report  read by the   
OL,7,Fnewsreader  Presentation would have  
OL,8,Fshown the caption tweeted by Reg and  
OL,9,Fplayed somber music. At some point,   
OL,10,Ffurther news reports would have been  
OL,11,Fbroadcast.                            
OL,13,FBack to the present. The following days
OL,14,Fwill be very demanding for the BBC's  
OL,15,Fjournalists and others engaged in     
OL,16,Fspecial programmes.                   
OL,18,FPresentation will also have to remain 
OL,19,Fcompletely on the ball. Even one simple
OL,20,Fmistake could be seized upon by the   
OL,21,FBBC's enemies.                        
